  <chapter role="api-reference">
      <title>Summary of Changes</title>
      <para>
          This extension allows for a variety of capabilities for the global auth system e.g impersonation.
      </para>
      <section>
          <title>New Headers</title>
          <para>None.</para>
      </section>
      <section>
          <title>New Faults</title>
          <para>None.</para>
      </section>
      <section>
          <title>New Resources</title>
          <para>
              The new resources that are defined as part of this extension are listed below.
          </para>
          <resources xmlns="http://wadl.dev.java.net/2009/02">
              <resource href="RAX-GA.wadl#impersonation-tokens"/>
          </resources>
      </section>
      <section>
          <title>New Elements</title>
          <para>
              The samples of new elements that are defined as a part of this extension are listed below.
          </para>
          <example>
              <title>Impersonator Sample XML</title>
              <programlisting language="xml">
                    <?db-font-size 95% ?><xi:include href="../../formattedsamples/keystone/Impersonator.xml" parse="text"/>
               </programlisting>
          </example>
          <example>
